data.description: Welcome to 1271 N Elvira St. Nuzzled within the highly coveted town of Auburn, this residence enjoys a tranquil and quiet street, perfect for those seeking a serene neighborhood ambiance.   Notable for its attached one-car garage, this property ensures convenient and secure parking.   Inside, an inviting and comfortable living space unfolds, offering three bedrooms, a bonus room in the basement, and a well-appointed bathroom. The basement already features a functional toilet, presenting an excellent opportunity to add a second bathroom should you desire.  Buying a home with updated features is always a delight, and this property doesn't disappoint. The previous owner has implemented various upgrades, including new windows, flooring, and a remodeled bathroom. Furthermore, a brand-new air conditioning unit was installed in 2021, ensuring optimal comfort during the sweltering summer months.  For families with children, this home is situated in Washburn Rural school district. Don't let this incredible opportunity pass you by.
